description: You can count on the delicious chicken dishes from Jackpot Chicken to totally hit the spot. With a menu that features favorites like Hawaiian Chicken Tacos, Chicken Skewers with applewood smoked bacon, Jerk Chicken Sliders, Wings, and so much more, you Clevelanders are guaranteed to get the best cluck for your buck at this cool yellow truck. Appease your inner poultry fan by eating at Jackpot Chicken, because you know, “Winner, Winner, Chicken Dinner!”
name: Jackpot Chicken Food Truck
